Summary: Spherical object shows up hovering and moving from a video. Link attached.
divs: sighting details i was off-roading with three other jeeps at the rausch creek park in tremont, pa yesterday, 12\17\11. i did not notice the sphere while on the trail, but after checking back through the videos that we took, i noticed it. see [link moved to fi section\cms\tg] it's probably a reflection from within the jeep. but, i have not been able to figure it out since the video was not taken from within my jeep.
